      "span_text": "OTU clustering (at 97% similarity) was performed using the VSEARCH distance-based greedy clustering algorithm  within mothur (updated here to v1.40.5 to fix an error in the mothur implementation of VSEARCH clustering) rather than the default Opticlust algorithm (Westcott and Schloss 2017) because of its lower memory requirement and higher speed on this size of dataset."
